Class NotConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • adql.query.constraint.NotConstraint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class NotConstraint
extends java.lang.Object
implements ADQLConstraint
    Lets apply the logical operator NOT on any constraint.
    Version:
    1.4 (06/2015)
    Author:
    Grégory Mantelet (CDS;ARI)
